It appears that your kernel does not support the VDD levels sysfs interface. Please install a kernel that supports this feature in order to continue

For developers:
Supported sysfs interfaces are vdd_levels and UV_mV_tables
Want to add support for voltage adjusting in your kernel? Find a VDD patch on Github/Google for your device, apply it to your kernel source and build it. Don't forget to enable it in your config!
